title: Ghosts - Best of Coast to Coast AM - 10/31/22

description:
George Noory and psychic medium Mary Ann Winkowski explore her experiences with ghosts which began when she was a child visiting a funeral home, debate why spirits don't want to leave after they've died, and whether we should be afraid of them.
